				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Santander Finally Gets the Message on Capital</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Fiona Maharg-Bravo			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2015-01-08T19:45:34+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">January 8, 2015 2:45 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">January 8, 2015 2:45 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content">
	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2015/01/08/santander-finally-gets-the-message-on-capital/" data-title="Santander Finally Gets the Message on Capital" data-description="The Spanish lender had resisted raising equity. Now the new executive chairwoman, Ana Patricia BotÃ­n, has shown that she can decisively break with her fatherâs legacy, says Fiona Maharg-Bravo of Reuters Breakingviews. ">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
